{"tid":472712,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家支持下社區蜘蛛俠🙈🕷","createTime":"2017-11-18T13:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T05:41:38.000Z","uid":156348,"like":1488,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"a5539f6ebe884b9b9c7ca5ef3761873a0e79dae0","tid":472712,"uid":156348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:22:44.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知應該po去邊個台<br />\n <br />\n前幾日係旺角見到有人扮蜘蛛俠係到俾人影相，就貪得意去圍觀下影下相啦，見到佢個ig就follow埋啦，同時都好好奇點解佢要咁做，原因好有意義！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/211713_80477804de4cee4c72ed19285a80ad93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F211713_80477804de4cee4c72ed19285a80ad93.jpg&h=678dec20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/211714_db34b098ffbcb3520cf09a8f0c971379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F211714_db34b098ffbcb3520cf09a8f0c971379.jpg&h=a7fd01aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n其實好多人都想幫下個社會，但可能大多數都缺乏時間，但更多嘅係差個機會去幫人。<br />\n <br />\n大家唔好話佢傻或者自己都未搞掂付出乜，冇人係絕對地不利己只利他人，打哩個post亦唔係逼大家一定要為社會做事，我付出時邊個幫我係咪先，但只係見到有人只係想氹下小朋友同大家開心，都想宣傳下，鼓勵下。<br />\n <br />\n大家唔洗付出多，只有得閒見到佢say個hi，同佢打打氣，同身邊啲frd提及下有個人為下一代付出緊❤️<br />\n <br />\n順便follow下佢，有時間嘅就係ig問下睇下有咩幫到手啦💖<br />\n<br />\n佢ig係 : hkcspider<br />\n <br />\n多謝大家睇哂成篇嘢"},{"pid":"f7881f0b0cf45c0ed8c05d237aa14f41b6be69b2","tid":472712,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c419b754f0d4236fa443a54d49f74fe507c5233","tid":472712,"uid":838,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"件衫都幾專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"f47354942b2b4dbddeff354aca353e03ec782310","tid":472712,"uid":15345,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"